ActEmergency Management Act
SubjectNo. 117 - (BC) Provincial Emergencies Financial Assistance Order
PrecisPROVINCIAL EMERGENCY FINANCIAL ASSISTANCE ORDER NO. 117 - which makes a declaration of federal concern and authorizes the federal government to provide financial assistance to the province of BRITISH COLUMBIA with respect to damages that occurred from January 6, 2009 to January 8, 2009, in the Capital, Fraser Valley, and Greater Vancouver Regional Districts.
